They believe that the earth is flat !

00:00:10.030 --> 00:00:16.000
The flat earth society believes that the earth
is a flat disc !

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.130
On the map, The north pole is right at the
centre

00:00:18.130 --> 00:00:20.250
The continents and oceans are around it.

00:00:20.250 --> 00:00:25.269
At the edges, there is a 150 foot wall holding
the oceans

00:00:25.269 --> 00:00:29.460
They believe apollo moon landing were complete
hoax.

00:00:29.460 --> 00:00:34.960
because the US government wanted to win the
space race against russia

00:00:34.960 --> 00:00:41.000
The flat earth map is exactly identical to
the map printed on United Nations Flag.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:43.600
Interesting, isn't it?

00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:47.910
