have diameter about only 32 miles across.

00:00:55.890 --> 00:01:01.620
They believe that the sun n the moon revolve
around the earth just 3000 miles up in the

00:01:01.620 --> 00:01:02.620
sky.

00:01:02.620 --> 00:01:05.350
