and the moon.

00:01:05.350 --> 00:01:15.340
According to flat earth society, gravity is
created because the disc we live on, is constantly

00:01:15.340 --> 00:01:16.340
moving UP !

00:01:16.340 --> 00:01:21.479
If you throw a ball upwards, the ball isnt
coming down, instead you are moving up at

00:01:21.479 --> 00:01:22.770
9.8 m/s sq.

00:01:22.770 --> 00:01:30.090
The round earth scientist says that earth
is spinning at very high rate.

00:01:30.090 --> 00:01:37.329
The flat earth people say, if that were true,
then everything on earth would be thrown off

00:01:37.329 --> 00:01:39.520
